data.description: This amazing Spring Arbor lakefront house is looking for its new owner. It has incredible panoramic views that you won't be able to take your eyes off of.  Take a walk down to your private dock and don't forget your fishing pole.  Sit outside on the large deck or around the fire pit and watch the wildlife on and around the lake. Stay warm inside with the cozy gas fireplace.  Having company? There's room for everyone. Bright, open space on the main floor for entertaining, open kitchen with large island, plenty of bedrooms and even another living room and kitchenette in the finished, walkout  basement. Need storage? You won't be able to fill all the closets in this house. Major updates have already been done. It's ready for you to move in and enjoy. All furniture in pics is negotiable. Call today for your private showing.  Currently with an assumable 2.5% loan.
